span.p:
POST /dca/collectors/c_*/automate_template
{ description, urls (max 1) }
→ { id: ia_*, queued }

POST /dca/collectors/c_*/refactor_template
{ prompt, custom_input }
→ heal job ia_*

POST /dca/trigger?collector=c_*&queue_next=1
BATCH async
body: array of {url}
→ { collection_id: j_*, start_eta }

POST /dca/trigger_immediate?collector=c_*
REALTIME async
body: {url}
→ { response_id: z* }
